definition: to fill in a form/to write data in a box (on a questionnaire or web form)
to fill or stuff/(of a form etc) to fill in

sentences.english: You need to fill out registration card.
Please fill in this deposit slip first.
sentences.chinese: 請先填寫這張存款憑條。

sentences.english: Please complete registration form below and turn into your teacher or PTA .
sentences.chinese: 請詳細填寫報名表後交給班級老師或家長會。

sentences.english: Entry form is invalid if not properly completed or with insufficient supporting materials.
sentences.chinese: 報名表填寫不清或資料不齊者，一概視爲無效。

sentences.english: Please use additional sheet on Part B4 if required.
sentences.chinese: 如表格空位不夠，請加B4段表格填寫。

sentences.english: Fill the scoop lightly using the built-in leveler.
sentences.chinese: 填寫勺輕輕使用內置的勻染劑。

sentences.english: Fill out each box on the form on a 1-5 scale.
sentences.chinese: 按照一到五的等級來填寫表格。

sentences.english: Fill out the form and follow the instructions to activate your account.
sentences.chinese: 按要求填寫表格，並激活自己的帳號。

sentences.english: Put the request form and check in a separate sealed bad to keep them dry.
sentences.chinese: 把所填寫的表格單獨入與一個自封袋中，保證其乾淨。

sentences.english: Fill up Maritime Declaration of Health.
Please read the Notes before Application before filling out this application form.
sentences.chinese: 填寫報名表前，請先詳讀招生簡章上的報名注意事項。

sentences.english: If you have any problem(s) filling in this form, please contact your account opening branch.
sentences.chinese: 如於填寫本表格時有任何疑問，請向開戶分行查詢。

sentences.english: Hm, thank you. Now, please fill in this form.
sentences.chinese: 完成交費的考生，請填寫好報名表，填好後提交。

sentences.english: Prices on the item tender offer sheet shall be filled out in the following manner.
sentences.chinese: 投標分項報價表上的價格應按下列方式分開填寫。

sentences.english: What if I did not complete my candidate number?
sentences.chinese: 如果我沒有填寫完整的准考證號在答題卡上怎麼辦？

sentences.english: I have finished the application form for SRTP now.
sentences.chinese: 今天終於忙完了SRTP的申請表填寫。

definition: to present/to give/to hand over/to hand in/to lay before
email/abbr. for 電子郵件|电子邮件[dian4 zi3 you2 jian4]
